Rezzolla et al. (2018), we recall that quasi-universal relations
exist between the masses of uniformly rotating stellar models
along the stability line to BH formation and the correspond-
ing dimensionless angular momentum 𝑗coll normalised to the
maximum (Keplerian) one 𝑗Kep (Breu & Rezzolla 2016). We
